      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software version control and documented test suite must be in place for all CFD solver components.",
      "rationale": "OpenFOAM v8 used with version-controlled case files in institutional git repository. Automated regression tests confirm solver build integrity. Achieves Gradation 2 requirement for MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations via manufactured solution or benchmark comparison.",
      "rationale": "Code verification performed against lid-driven cavity benchmark (Re=1000) and Taylor-Green vortex. Results match published reference data within 0.5% for velocity profiles. Gradation 2 satisfied."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Discretization error must be quantified and shown to be below 5% for primary QoI (shear stress distribution).",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted (4.2M, 11.7M, 28.4M cells). GCI analysis yields discretization error of 2.1% for volume-averaged scalar stress. Achieves Gradation 3, exceeding MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
