    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The CFD hemolysis model for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is accepted for the CPB COU at MRL 2. Seven credibility factors were assessed and the model was found to meet or exceed requirements across software quality assurance, code verification, discretization error, test conditions, output comparison, and relevance factors. The remaining six factors were scoped out as not required at MRL 2. Overall credibility is sufficient to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
